</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:35
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='624601' id='t-624601'>This brings us back to our network
and to the antennas</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='627675' id='t-627675'>on the roof of the Swiss Embassy in Berlin</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='629929' id='t-629929'>and the &quot;Can You Hear Me?&quot; project.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='632725' id='t-632725'>We should not take it for granted
to be boundlessly connected.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='635959' id='t-635959'>We should start making
